## Extra Pro Tips & Warnings 2026

- Use GitHub Desktop or VS Code for easier local work (later step)
- Enable GitHub Pages for free live demos
- Add .gitignore files to avoid junk commits
- Write meaningful commit messages
- Never pay for "guaranteed internships" or "GitHub boosting" — scams!
- Avoid spammy low-effort AI-generated PRs — many projects ban them now (zero tolerance in 2026)
- Combine: GitHub + LinkedIn + Internshala = maximum shots
- Share progress: "Just merged my first PR!" posts get attention

Consistency beats talent when talent is inconsistent.

